can consumer technology,

00:21:56.610 --> 00:22:00.260
or how can technology in
general, like Google, Facebook,

00:22:00.260 --> 00:22:01.940
everything here
in Silicon Valley,

00:22:01.940 --> 00:22:05.347
really help accelerate
social change ?

00:22:05.347 --> 00:22:06.805
MATTHIEU RICARD:
Well, you see, you

00:22:06.805 --> 00:22:10.721
must remember once when
I did a small book called

00:22:10.721 --> 00:22:12.720
"The Art of Meditation"--
or I think it's called

00:22:12.720 --> 00:22:20.810
