started with the spark.

00:22:40.810 --> 00:22:43.470
And there's no war,
or discrimination,

00:22:43.470 --> 00:22:48.790
or massacre that didn't start
with hatred, or at least

00:22:48.790 --> 00:22:50.660
with devaluing others.

00:22:50.660 --> 00:22:54.320
If you value others and
you are concern by others,

00:22:54.320 --> 00:22:58.860
then how can you exert harm
if you are genuinely concerned

00:22:58.860 --> 00:23:00.860
with the well-being of somebody?

00:23:00.860 --> 00:23:02.490
So it did start with the mind.

00:23:02.490 --> 00:23:05.010
There's no war that didn't
start with someone, somebody,

00:23:05.010 --> 00:23:14.750
a group contagiously having this
dehumanization of the other,

00:23:14.750 --> 00:23:17.180
reducing them the
state of thinking

00:23:17.180 --> 00:23:21.490
they are like animals, inferior,
and so forth and so forth.

00:23:21.490 --> 00:23:23.660
So that's why.

00:23:23.660 --> 00:23:26.620
The fact that immediately
a change of mind,

00:23:26.620 --> 00:23:29.380
first, would not solve
immediately a conflict

00:23:29.380 --> 00:23:31.600
that is raging somewhere.

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:33.910
But after all, conflicts
are made with people.

00:23:33.910 --> 00:23:36.280
People have different
states of mind.

00:23:36.280 --> 00:23:39.090
And that's exactly what
I mentioned earlier

00:23:39.090 --> 00:23:42.440
about the articulation point
between individual and societal

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:43.700
change.

00:23:43.700 --> 00:23:47.310
A culture that is based
on nonviolent values,

00:23:47.310 --> 00:23:49.990
on compassion and
altruistic love,

00:23:49.990 --> 00:23:52.910
it's much more likely
that they will not

00:23:52.910 --> 00:23:55.740
be resort to violence
to solve conflicts.

00:23:55.740 --> 00:24:00.310
They will not impose
terrible things onto others.

00:24:00.310 --> 00:24:02.420
So it start with someone.

00:24:02.420 --> 00:24:06.650
Then it grows to family, the
community, the working place,

00:24:06.650 --> 00:24:09.250
the society, the
village, the culture.

00:24:09.250 --> 00:24:12.260
And then culture can
become also contagious

00:24:12.260 --> 00:24:14.100
or succeed better than
other cultures, which

00:24:14.100 --> 00:24:18.400
are more individualistic,
everyone against everyone.

00:24:18.400 --> 00:24:20.690
So the evolution of
culture can favor that,

00:24:20.690 --> 00:24:23.240
and it starts with the people.

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:25.800
A society is made of people.

00:24:25.800 --> 00:24:31.900
So if you have a culture that is
nonviolent because generations

00:24:31.900 --> 00:24:35.040
of people have
cultivated those virtues.

00:24:35.040 --> 00:24:37.860
And if someone is
promoting violence,

00:24:37.860 --> 00:24:41.870
then your children will also
grow in that environment.

00:24:41.870 --> 00:24:46.430
So it's not the
immediate, magic solution.

00:24:46.430 --> 00:24:49.480
But it's the only way that we
gradually change individuals

00:24:49.480 --> 00:24:52.450
and by extension society.

00:24:52.450 --> 00:24:55.540
So we should not worry
that immediately I

00:24:55.540 --> 00:24:58.140
may not have an effect, some
kind of magic vibes going

00:24:58.140 --> 00:24:59.520
to solve conflicts.

00:24:59.520 --> 00:25:02.210
But the more there are people
thinking that way, especially

00:25:02.210 --> 00:25:04.370
in the global world,
virtual world,

00:25:04.370 --> 00:25:06.410
where altruistic
people have a tendency

00:25:06.410 --> 00:25:10.265
to get together and cooperate,
while the free-riders,

00:25:10.265 --> 00:25:11.750
the really selfish
guys, they kick

00:25:11.750 --> 00:25:13.460
each others' legs all day long.

00:25:13.460 --> 00:25:16.570
So as a group, they have
a selective disadvantage

00:25:16.570 --> 00:25:18.540
to a group of altruistics
who cooperate.

00:25:18.540 --> 00:25:19.420
That's clear.

00:25:19.420 --> 00:25:21.490
All the models have shown that.

00:25:21.490 --> 00:25:23.590
So we should not
get discouraged.

00:25:23.590 --> 00:25:26.870
It's one by one, thought after
thought, emotion after emotion,

00:25:26.870 --> 00:25:28.480
individual after individual.

00:25:28.480 --> 00:25:30.670
And somehow you
create a culture.

00:25:30.670 --> 00:25:34.040
That may take a few
years or some whatever,

00:25:34.040 --> 00:25:36.570
but you can make a real
difference, because everyone

00:25:36.570 --> 00:25:37.760
can make a difference.

00:25:37.760 --> 00:25:42.780
And that difference ripples out.

00:25:42.780 --> 00:25:45.460
So that's why movements started.

00:25:45.460 --> 00:25:48.350
When I first came here, I think
there was not much question

00:25:48.350 --> 00:25:50.447
about [? G Pose ?] and--

