So mindfulness,
people accepted that.

00:31:14.030 --> 00:31:16.890
And it's thanks to Jon
Kabat-Zinn and all this work.

00:31:16.890 --> 00:31:19.250
Now in the clinical world
and corporate world,

00:31:19.250 --> 00:31:22.370
it's widely accepted,
a mindful revolution.

00:31:22.370 --> 00:31:25.470
