probably by the right people,

00:31:25.470 --> 00:31:29.380
you could imagine using
it for just efficiency,

00:31:29.380 --> 00:31:33.740
cold efficiency, so therefore
they make a mindful psychopath.

00:31:33.740 --> 00:31:37.450
So that's why I think caring
is very acceptable, politically

00:31:37.450 --> 00:31:39.880
correct, you could say.

00:31:39.880 --> 00:31:42.940
And therefore, the
notion of caring,

00:31:42.940 --> 00:31:45.710
I think, in now
world I don't see

00:31:45.710 --> 00:31:48.970
why it should meet any
resistance, why you would say

00:31:48.970 --> 00:31:52.410
that compassion,
altruism-- although it's

00:31:52.410 --> 00:31:55.000
the same thing--
